          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Microwave-rice-1675247654394-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Microwave-rice-1675247654394-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>Thai green curry stock</strong> to the pan along with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> and cook for 2-3 min, or until the prawns are cooked through and the sauce has thickened slightly – this is your <strong>Thai green jumbo prawn curry</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
